[new:]
HexviewMode

[new:]
As of March 2020, the best hex mode for Emacs appears to be nhexl-mode (https://elpa.gnu.org/packages/nhexl-mode.html). It comes with nhexl-nibble-edit-mode, which lets you edit the hex codes directly (as requested above).
-- Ivar

